#: ../../user_interface/menu/settings_menu/configure_kdenlive.rst:260
msgid ""
"**Processing and transcode jobs**: This is experimental and was removed in "
"ver 0.9.10. This number was passed to melts *real_time* consumer property. "
"This parameter increases the number of threads the program uses for video "
"decoding and processing (but not encoding which is controlled via :ref:"
"`render`).  See `mlt doco <https://www.mltframework.org/faq/#does-mlt-take-"
"advantage-of-multiple-cores-or-how-do-i-enable-parallel-processing>`_. Using "
"this has potential side effects - see `this <https://forum.kde.org/viewtopic."
"php%3Ff=265&t=122140.html#p317318>`_ forum post from the author of the Melt "
"program."
msgstr ""
"**Treballs de processament i transcodificació**: Això era experimental i es "
"va eliminar a la ver. 0.9.10. Aquest nombre es passava per a fusionar la "
"propietat de consum *temps real*. Aquest paràmetre incrementa el nombre de "
"fils que usa el programa per a descodificar vídeo i processar (però no per a "
"codificar, que es controla a través de :ref:`render`). Vegeu la "
"`documentació del «mlt» <https://www.mltframework.org/faq/#does-mlt-take-"
"advantage-of-multiple-cores-or-how-do-i-enable-parallel-processing>`_. El "
"seu ús té efectes col·laterals potencials: vegeu `aquest <https://forum.kde."
"org/viewtopic.php%3Ff=265&t=122140.html#p317318>`_ article del fòrum de "
"l'autor del programa Melt."

